<i>adverb</i>: 다정히 [다정히], 다정스레 [다정스레] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>다정히 [다정히]</dt><br>
<dd>lovingly; caringly</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 따뜻하고 정이 많게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a warm and caring manner.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>다정스레 [다정스레]</dt><br>
<dd>lovingly; caringly</dd><br>
<dd>정이 많고 친근하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In an affectionate and caring manner.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>